OL,3,CYorkshire Water announces hosepipe ban
OL,5,FYorkshire Water has announced a
OL,6,Fhosepipe ban will come into force
OL,7,Flater this week after the region
OL,8,Frecorded its driest and warmest spring
OL,9,Fon record.
OL,11,FFrom Friday, people won't be permitted
OL,12,Fto use hosepipes to water their
OL,13,Fgardens, wash their cars or for any
OL,14,Fother activities.
OL,16,FReservoirs in Yorkshire are currently
OL,17,Fat 55.8%, which is 26.1% lower than
OL,18,Fthey usually would be at this time of
OL,19,Fyear.
