OL,3,CYorkshire Water announces hosepipe ban
OL,5,FThe Environment Agency officially
OL,6,Fdeclared a drought in the county in
OL,7,FJune and forecasters are predicting a
OL,8,Fwarm summer.
OL,10,FYorkshire Water's director of water,
OL,11,FDave Kaye, said: "Introducing these
OL,12,Frestrictions is not a decision we have
OL,13,Ftaken lightly, and we've been doing
OL,14,Feverything we can to avoid having to
OL,15,Fput them in place.
OL,17,F"Our region experienced an extremely
OL,18,Fdry spring, which resulted in the
OL,19,Fregion entering drought status in June.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
