OL,3,CYorkshire Water announces hosepipe ban
OL,5,F"Usually, spring is a time when our
OL,6,Fgroundwater sources and reservoirs
OL,7,Fcontinue to be topped-up by changeable
OL,8,Fweather, but this has not been the
OL,9,Fcase in 2025, with our reservoir
OL,10,Fstocks falling since the last week of
OL,11,FJanuary."
OL,13,FThe activities under the ban are:
OL,15,FBusinesses will be allowed to use a
OL,16,Fhosepipe if it is related to a
OL,17,Fcommercial purpose.
