OL,5,FMeanwhile blue badge holders, those on
OL,6,FYorkshire Water's Priority Services
OL,7,FRegister or WaterSure tariff for
OL,8,Fmedical reasons, are also excluded
OL,9,Ffrom the restrictions.
OL,11,FYorkshire Water say restrictions will
OL,12,Fstay in place until the region has
OL,13,Fseen significant rainfall but warned
OL,14,Fthat they could last into the winter.
